# Privacy Policy for Gym AI

Last updated: October 6, 2025

## Information We Collect
- Email address (for authentication)
- Display name
- Workout data (stored locally and optionally synced)
- Profile information (if you choose to share)
- Social interactions (posts, comments, likes, follows)

## How We Use Your Information
- To provide and maintain our service
- To authenticate your account
- To enable social features
- To improve our app

## Data Storage
- Local data stored on your device using SQLite
- Cloud sync via Supabase (optional)
- Images stored on Supabase Storage

## Third-Party Services
- Supabase (authentication and database)
- Facebook Login (authentication only)
- Google OAuth (authentication only)
- Apple Sign In (authentication only)

## Your Rights
- Access your data
- Delete your account and data
- Opt-out of data collection

## Contact
Email: klaus.dev@outlook.com

## Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy from time to time.
